Dialogue: 0,00:00:06.92,00:00:12.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)伝説の三忍\N自来也も ついに死す。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the legendary Sannin...\NJiraiya is no more...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:12.06,00:00:17.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,我らに この秘密がなければ\N勝てはしなかっただろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we didn't have this secret,\Nwe could not have won.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:17.41,00:00:21.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)さすがは我が師と\N讃えておこう。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us praise him as our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:21.08,00:00:24.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ところで… そろそろ出てこい。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...\Nyou can come out.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:26.76,00:00:29.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)かなり かかったね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure took you a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent was Jiraiya,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:29.27,00:00:32.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,相手は\Nあの自来也だったのだからな。
Dialogue: 0,00:00:32.17,00:00:34.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,とんだ邪魔が入った。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some interference we got.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:34.94,00:00:39.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,マダラから 九尾を狩るように\N命を受けていたんだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm under orders from Madara\Nto capture the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:39.12,00:00:44.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それじゃあさ 九尾を狩るのを\N見てみたいから一緒に行こうよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... I'd love to see\Nthe Nine-Tails captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.46,00:00:47.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ダメだ。 オレは 別の戦いを見にいく。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm going to watch another battle.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:47.80,00:00:51.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,え～っ…。\Nうるさい 黙れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:51.14,00:00:53.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)どの戦いを見んの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which battle is that?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.49,00:01:00.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)それは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle between...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:04.30,00:01:07.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(水月)大丈夫かね？ サスケのヤツ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sasuke is okay...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:07.11,00:01:09.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(香燐)何がだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the first Akatsuki hideout\Nis a bull's-eye?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:09.04,00:01:13.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁のアジト探索 １発目が\Nビンゴだったらって話さ。
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.89,00:01:17.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(重吾)イタチが このアジトに\Nいるとでも言うのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying Itachi is\Ninside this hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "what if?"
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.13,00:01:22.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(水月)さあね。 いたらって話。
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.81,00:01:26.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,相当なやり手なんだろ？ イタチって。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This Itachi is supposed to\Nbe really strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:26.15,00:01:30.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケにかぎって\Nやられるなんてこと あるわけ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Sasuke\Ncould lose to...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:30.02,00:01:36.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オレたちも まさかのときのこと\N考えたほうがいいのかもね。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should be thinking about\Na worst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.17,00:01:39.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サスケ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:39.07,00:01:44.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウチは ここから中の様子を探る。\N何かあったら すぐに向かうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check out\Nthe inside from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, we're going in!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:44.05,00:01:48.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はあ？ 何 急に\N仕切りだしちゃってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why're you taking over\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.19,00:01:51.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,キミは サスケのこととなると\Nすぐ ムキになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Sasuke,\Nyou go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.10,00:01:56.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,べ… 別に ウチは ムキになど…\Nやっ… やんのか！ このヤロウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going... You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.54,00:01:59.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら オレは 鳥たちに頼んで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask the birds to\Nscour the area
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.45,00:02:02.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,周囲から敵が追ってこないか\N見張らせておこう。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and look out for\Nthe enemy's approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... Both of you...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.36,00:02:07.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ったく どいつもコイツも…。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:07.50,00:02:10.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《マジメだねぇ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're so diligent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:02:16.85,00:02:19.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ナルト)こっちも ニセモノだってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a fake too...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:19.75,00:02:22.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケのニオイを\N追っかけてるはずなのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chasing after Sasuke's scent, yet...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.73,00:02:25.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,敵が 一枚上手ってことか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the enemy is\None step ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.87,00:02:30.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから 敵の陽動以上に\N数で対抗してんだろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're compensating\Nfor their diversions with numbers!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:30.04,00:02:32.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こっちは あらかた調べつくした。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've checked this side thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.95,00:02:37.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いったん 本体に戻って\N情報を渡したほうがいいかもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We should report this to the original.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.57,00:02:45.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)どうした？ ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The south forest only had dummies.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:45.91,00:02:48.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,南の森には ダミーしか\Nいなかったみてえだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:48.58,00:02:50.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:50.51,00:02:52.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(キバ)なに落ち込んでんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so depressed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You never give up.\NIsn't that your ninja way?!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:52.92,00:02:55.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あきらめねえのが\Nテメエの忍道じゃなかったのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.82,00:02:58.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)そうよ ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:00.73,00:03:02.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the chakra I've restored\Nto increase the Shadow Clones.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:02.74,00:03:06.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,回復したチャクラの分だけ\Nさらに影分身を増やしていくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.22,00:03:12.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな 頼んだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you all!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:12.73,00:03:15.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,任せとけって！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Leave it to us!\N- Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:42.62,00:03:44.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)来たか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:46.49,00:03:48.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(サスケ)誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me... Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.50,00:03:53.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)オレだ… サスケ。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.18,00:04:01.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少し背が伸びたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown a bit taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're still the same.\NEven those cold eyes...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:03.93,00:04:08.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタは 相変わらずだな。\Nその冷たい目も。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.27,00:04:14.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,前のように 大声で がむしゃらに\N突っ込んではこないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not going to scream and attack\Nlike you did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just as you said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.31,00:04:30.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタの言ったとおり\Nアンタを恨み 憎み➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've hated you... and resented you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.18,00:04:34.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そして アンタを\N殺すためだけにオレは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the singular purpose\N{\i1}of killing you, I...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:38.33,00:04:40.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オレは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have lived my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.20,00:04:44.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,生きてきた！
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.35,00:04:51.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,千鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chidori?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.29,00:04:54.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタを殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will kill you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:54.23,00:05:02.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うお～っ！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:02.65,00:05:05.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(死ね！))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.33,00:05:17.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フン。 アンタはオレのことを\N何もわかっちゃいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know a thing about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How much hatred I carry inside me...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.03,00:05:34.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どれほどの憎しみを\N心のなかに抱えているか。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.71,00:05:38.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのおかげで\Nどれほど強くなっているか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And how strong I have become\Nbecause of that hatred.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:42.06,00:05:45.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタは オレのことを\N何もわかっちゃいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know me at all.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.71,00:06:10.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,強くなったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become... strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the Uchiha hideout alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:24.07,00:06:26.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,１人でうちはのアジトに来い。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:26.58,00:06:29.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そこで決着をつけさせてやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you settle things there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:38.77,00:06:40.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(水月)サスケ！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.65,00:06:47.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,命令があるまで\N動くなと言ったはずだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to move until\Nyou received orders.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:47.96,00:06:52.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,香燐が 他のチャクラを感じたって\N言ったから 気になってね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin said she sensed another chakra,\Nso we were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Feathers?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:56.14,00:06:58.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,羽根？
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.95,00:07:04.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オレについて来い。 行くぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me. Let's go!
