Dialogue: 0,00:09:00.68,00:09:06.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(トビ)いい流れだ。\Nあとは 次の脱皮でヘビのままか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming along nicely. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you still emerge as a snake?\NOr will you transform into a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:06.55,00:09:10.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それとも タカに変わるか見ものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall see, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.36,00:09:12.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ。
Dialogue: 0,00:09:16.71,00:09:18.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,同じチャクラがあちこちにあるぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The same chakra is all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:18.64,00:09:21.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうなってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:21.05,00:09:23.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,進路を変えるかい？ サスケ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we change course, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:23.39,00:09:26.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,気にするな。 真っ直ぐに突っ切る。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore it. We'll forge straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:26.73,00:09:29.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よかった。 遠回りは疲れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Taking the long way\Nwould've been tiring.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.76,00:09:46.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:50.04,00:09:52.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なに？ 今の。\N影分身だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shadow Clone.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.38,00:09:54.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルトか。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, eh?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:54.32,00:09:56.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《うっとうしいヤツだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a pest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.25,00:09:59.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,多重影分身。 なるほど。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi-Shadow Clones... I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:59.26,00:10:02.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あちこちにいる\N同じチャクラの正体は今のヤツか。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The same chakra I sense all over\Nthe place belongs to him.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:04.97,00:10:06.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,見つけた！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:09.75,00:10:12.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よくやったぜ！ どっちだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way?!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:12.42,00:10:14.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:14.36,00:10:18.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《もう逃がさねえぞ サスケ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not letting you get away\N{\i1}this time, Sasuke!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.45,00:10:30.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これは？ すごいチャクラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A humongous chakra!\NAnd it's fast! Incoming!!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:30.12,00:10:32.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに 速い。 くる！
Dialogue: 0,00:10:45.32,00:10:47.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Sasuke-kun may go beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:47.25,00:10:52.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)ここからは\Nサスケ君一人で行ってください。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:52.10,00:10:54.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イタチさんの命令でしてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Itachi-san's orders.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:54.77,00:10:58.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,他の方々は ここで\N待っていてもらいましょうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you are welcome\Nto wait here.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:58.64,00:11:03.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかった。 小隊で動いていたのは\Nもともと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Besides, we were only\Ntraveling as a platoon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to prevent interference\Nfor my showdown...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.12,00:11:06.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,１対１に邪魔が\N入らないようにするためだからな。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:06.79,00:11:08.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ちょうどいい。\Nサスケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:08.73,00:11:12.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それはダメだ。 コイツを倒して\N全員で行くんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take him down and\Ngo in together!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:12.31,00:11:16.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私は 戦う気などありませんがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you insist on going with him,\NI will show no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:16.15,00:11:19.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,無理やり通るというなら\N容赦しませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:19.82,00:11:24.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,香燐 おとなしくしていろ。\Nこれは オレの復讐だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin... Stay put.\NThis is {\i1}my{\i0}  vendetta.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.50,00:11:26.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:32.85,00:11:38.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,干柿鬼鮫… そして 大刀 鮫肌。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshigaki Kisame...\NAnd the Great Shark Skin Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.19,00:11:45.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忘れたか？ 鬼灯満月の弟\N鬼灯水月だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Suigetsu Hozuki,\Nthe younger bother of Mangetsu Hozuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:45.71,00:11:51.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おぉ… 見違えましたよ。\N大きくなりましたね 水月。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I didn't recognize you!\NYou've grown, Suigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.82,00:11:56.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここで ただ サスケの帰りを\N待つのもなんだから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to just wait around\Nfor Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:56.16,00:12:00.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヒマつぶしに\N楽しく遊んでもらえないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me kill some time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and have some fun with you,\NKisame-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:00.67,00:12:02.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,鬼鮫先輩。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.61,00:12:06.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お兄さんと違い\Nやんちゃですねぇ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike your brother,\Nyou're quite cocky, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:06.01,00:12:09.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少し 削ってあげましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should grind you down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:09.85,00:12:13.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,水月！ サスケの言いつけを\N守らなくていいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu... Shouldn't we abide\Nby Sasuke's orders?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:13.73,00:12:16.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《のんきなこと\N言ってんじゃないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be stupid! You blockhead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.53,00:12:18.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この でくの坊が！》
Dialogue: 0,00:12:30.83,00:12:34.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな！ こっちだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, guys!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.17,00:12:36.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヒナタ)待って ナルト君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Naruto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:36.11,00:12:38.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《このチャクラは！》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This chakra...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.51,00:12:40.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうも～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:40.45,00:12:42.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どわっ！ なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.39,00:12:47.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ！ いやいや…\Nどうもどうも どうもっす！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now... How's it going there,\Nthere, and there?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:47.53,00:12:51.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんなところで\N木ノ葉の皆さんに ばったり！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine running into the Hidden Leaf\Nin a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:51.87,00:12:57.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかも… 二の四の六の…\N８対１とは間の悪い。 ハハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... It's two, four, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight against one. Such bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.75,00:13:01.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)その衣…\Nお前も 暁のメンバーだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That robe...\NYou're a member of the Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.39,00:13:06.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)コイツは カブトの残した\N暁のリストには載ってなかったが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he wasn't on the list\Nthat Kabuto left us.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:06.57,00:13:09.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アハ！ 新人なもんで。\Nどうもよろしく。\N(赤丸)ワン！ ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm a newbie. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:09.91,00:13:14.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(キバ)ヘッ！ ふざけやがって。\N余裕かましてんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Think you're funny?!\NDon't waste our time!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.08,00:13:17.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うかつな動きはするな。\Nまずは 様子を見る。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash. Study the situation first.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:17.96,00:13:21.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,数は 圧倒的に\Nこちらが有利なんだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we have him outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.70,00:13:26.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あらら… ナメられちゃってます？\Nボクのこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...\NAm I being underestimated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By you guys?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:30.21,00:13:32.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《シノ : これが 暁か…》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is an Akatsuki member...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:34.56,00:13:36.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サクラ : また 変なのが！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another weirdo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.49,00:13:39.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君を目の前にして\Nこう何度も 何度も…》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They keep getting between us and\N{\i1}Sasuke-kun over and over again!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:42.24,00:13:44.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.17,00:13:46.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,邪魔すんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.58,00:13:48.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,影分身！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shadow Clone?!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:48.52,00:13:50.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うわ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:50.45,00:13:52.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.46,00:13:54.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,な～んてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.60,00:13:58.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でやぁ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.54,00:14:00.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,はぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:00.47,00:14:05.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの小僧よりは マシに\Nその大刀を扱うようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you're more proficient\Nwith the blade than that kid.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:05.62,00:14:08.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,小僧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:08.29,00:14:10.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,再不斬先輩のことか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Zabuza-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:14.97,00:14:20.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,元来 私の大刀 鮫肌は\N斬り合う道具ではないんですがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My Great Shark Skin Sword was\Nnever intended for dueling, you know!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:23.79,00:14:28.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そりゃ こっちも同じ！\N斬るんじゃなくて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here. This one's...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:28.26,00:14:30.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,断つのさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for killing!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:33.61,00:14:38.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ！ 何が 楽しく遊ぶ だ！\N本気で殺し合ってるじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Have fun? As if!\NThey're dead serious!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:38.95,00:14:41.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おい 重吾！ お前からも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Jugo... Tell him...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:41.62,00:14:46.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。 ２人の戦いの邪魔を\Nするヤツは 近くにいないって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay... The birds are telling me
Dialogue: 0,00:14:46.47,00:14:48.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,小鳥たちも言ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one nearby who will interfere\Nwith their fighting.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:48.97,00:14:52.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《まったく…。\N仲間が こんな調子で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez... What if something happens\N{\i1}to Sasuke{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.31,00:14:55.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケに もしものことがあったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while these idiots are going at it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.22,00:14:58.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉だって\N追ってきてるっていうのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the Hidden Leaf are in pursuit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:58.19,00:15:00.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉の動きが止まった？》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Hidden Leaf have stopped?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:00.66,00:15:03.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(トビ)図に乗りすぎでしょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:03.17,00:15:06.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,キミみたいな子に\N何ができるってのかな!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what can a kid like you do?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:21.30,00:15:23.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト君…。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:23.64,00:15:25.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《よかった…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.58,00:15:29.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヒナタ！ ナルトなら あれくらい大丈夫。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto can handle the damage!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:31.39,00:15:35.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,敵から 目をそらさないで。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:35.00,00:15:36.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ありゃりゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Are you guys analyzing\Nmy strength right now?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:36.93,00:15:40.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もしかして ボクの力量とか\N観察されちゃったりしてとか？
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.88,00:15:43.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉の皆さんは抜け目ないな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf are very shrewd...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:43.68,00:15:48.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも 新人にしちゃ\Nやるほうでしょ？ ボクも。 ウフフフ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a newbie, I'm pretty good...\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.19,00:15:51.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルトの攻撃は\Nすべて スカされてますね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dodged every one\Nof Naruto's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:51.86,00:15:55.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,遊ばれてるね。 何が目的だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's toying with us.\NBut what is he after?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:01.22,00:16:07.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《チッ！ 大刀を操るパワーは\Nヤツのが ちょっと上か》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsk! He has a tad more power\N{\i1}in wielding the blade.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:07.03,00:16:09.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.40,00:16:11.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,一本調子ですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a monotone effort.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:11.34,00:16:15.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,再不斬より上だと言ったのは\N取り消しますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said about you\Nbeing better than Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:19.08,00:16:21.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くらえ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.96,00:16:26.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今のは惜しかったでしょ？ 先輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost got you there, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:26.70,00:16:29.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何を はしゃいでるんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so excited about?\NIs it your snack time?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:29.61,00:16:32.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ\Nおやつの時間じゃないのですか？
Dialogue: 0,00:16:32.58,00:16:35.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何を！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:35.38,00:16:40.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《チャクラが… ここまで消耗するほど\N使っていないはずなのに！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My chakra...\N{\i1}But I didn't use up that much yet!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:40.26,00:16:44.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私の鮫肌は チャクラを削り食らう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shark Skin Sword grinds\Nand absorbs chakra.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:44.90,00:16:47.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もっと\N賢いかと思っていましたが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be more observant.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:47.81,00:16:50.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう一度 試してみますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Care for another taste?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.78,00:16:54.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くっ！ コイツ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.25,00:16:58.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さてと… 何して遊びましょうか？\N木ノ葉の皆さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... What shall we play,\NHidden Leaf folks?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:58.76,00:17:02.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,テメエなんかと遊んでる暇はねえ！\Nそのとおり。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to waste\Non the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:02.64,00:17:06.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜなら サスケを\Nさっさと追わなければならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we have to go\Nafter Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.65,00:17:08.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ワン ワン！
Dialogue: 0,00:17:08.78,00:17:12.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,シノ！ お前は 前回のサスケ奪還任務は\N不参加だったからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino, you didn't get to go on\Nthe last mission to retrieve Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:12.96,00:17:14.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今回は頼むぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you this time!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:14.90,00:17:17.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サイ : 繋がり か…》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our bond, is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:17.30,00:17:21.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よし みんな！\Nさっさと終わらせよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... everyone.\NLet's end this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:23.18,00:17:26.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フォーメーションＢでいくよ みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go with Formation B, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:26.32,00:17:28.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オッス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:28.26,00:17:30.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(キバ)おう！\N(ヒナタ)はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:30.19,00:17:35.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだか 本気モードっすね！\Nこっちも 気合い 入れなくっちゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh? Seems you're serious.\NWell, I'd better get fired up.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:35.67,00:17:38.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,野郎！ ふざけやがって!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk... Quit kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:38.34,00:17:43.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト！ 今は フォーメーションに集中して。\Nあぁ わかってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, concentrate on the formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:43.22,00:17:45.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いくわよ。 キバ！ そっちも オーケー？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.\NKiba, are you ready on your side?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:45.52,00:17:48.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いつでも いいぜ！ なぁ？ 赤丸。\Nワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime. Right, Akamaru?!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:48.86,00:17:51.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それじゃ いくわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here goes!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:51.54,00:17:56.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しゃ～！ んなろ～!!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.21,00:17:59.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ありゃ～！\Nこりゃ また ずいぶん高く…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, so high...\NThat girl has such brute power.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:59.55,00:18:01.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,とんだ怪力少女！
Dialogue: 0,00:18:01.49,00:18:05.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ゲッ！ おとりに気をとられてる隙に\N３人で囲むつもり!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! They distracted me with the decoy...\NAnd now those three are surrounding me!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:05.90,00:18:08.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これじゃ どれをかわしたらいいか\Nわからないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know which one to dodge!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:08.80,00:18:11.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ちょ ちょ… ちょっと\Nそれって ずるいでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Say, that's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:11.58,00:18:14.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よそ見してる暇はねえ！\Nワン ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- No time for you to look!\N- Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:14.25,00:18:16.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんと！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:16.19,00:18:19.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しゃ～！ た～っ!!\Nオレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannaro! Shannaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Olay!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:19.59,00:18:23.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,３対１だなんて 木ノ葉の卑怯者！\N螺旋丸!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Three against one?!\NYou Hidden Leaf cowards!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:23.20,00:18:26.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ギョ ギョ ギョッ！\Nおとりじゃなかったの!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't the decoy?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.10,00:18:28.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やられ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me...!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:30.08,00:18:32.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:18:32.22,00:18:34.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,てない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:34.25,00:18:36.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍法 通せんぼの術！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art! Blockade Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.10,00:18:43.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まったく… みんなで やるなんて\N言っちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes... You said you were going\Nto do it all together...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:43.24,00:18:45.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,信じちゃったじゃないですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believed you!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:45.18,00:18:48.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな 止まるな！\N散り散りになって 強行突破だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Separate and force your way through!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:50.99,00:18:54.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あちゃ～！\Nに… 忍法… え～っと… もう!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear! N-Ninja Art...\NUmm... Geez!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:03.65,00:19:05.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだ？ この術は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of jutsu is that?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:05.65,00:19:08.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ！ ひらめいた!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! I'm going to name this jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:08.12,00:19:12.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この術は 忍法 モグラたたきの術と\N名づけよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Whack-A-Mole Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:12.63,00:19:15.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,たたく側と たたかれる側が\N逆だけどね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Except the roles for hitting are reversed...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.97,00:19:17.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先輩。
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.91,00:19:23.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ コイツは マジで倒していかないと\N先に進ませてくれないようだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we finish him off for good,\Nhe won't let us move forward.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:23.79,00:19:26.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:26.43,00:19:30.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ ねぇ ねぇ 次は何して遊ぶ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Say say... What shall we play next?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:32.24,00:19:35.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんな所で 足止め\Nくらってる場合じゃねえんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be wasting time\Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:35.94,00:19:40.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ わかっている。\N次は 戦闘フォーメーションＡでいくよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.\NWe'll go with Battle Formation A next.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:55.82,00:19:58.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《もう少しだ…。
