Dialogue: 0,00:21:43.37,00:21:46.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)ただ今より 350回突破を\N記念いたしまして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.60,NEP,,0,0,0,,It seems you've been waiting\Nfor this moment...
