Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.80,NEP,,0,0,0,,But the same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:48.64,00:21:50.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何やってんだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:21:50.58,00:21:53.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,主人公のオレが呼ばれてないって\Nどういうこった!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.80,NEP,,0,0,0,,Come...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:57.00,NEP,,0,0,0,,Recreate my death as you've seen it.
