Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It will begin shortly,\Nso please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In commemoration of passing\Nthe 350th episode...
Dialogue: 0,00:22:15.56,00:22:19.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも キリ番に出番なしなんて\N主人公失格ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:19.57,00:22:22.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃんまで そんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are... you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:22.41,00:22:25.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それでは 乾杯！\N(みんな)乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you guys invite me,\Nthe main character?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you weren't in Episode 350.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:25.88,00:22:28.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チクショウ…。\N(ヒナタ)ナルト君。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was just by coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,00:22:30.06,00:22:32.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ド… ドンマイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't in Episode 100\Nor Episode 300 either.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:32.00,00:22:35.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぐさめになってねえってばよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I don't want to be told\Nby a newcomer like you
